# which checks commit AUTHOR identity (each agent now commits under its own role identity) against
# the same map below. See docs/governance/ownership.md for the staged V&R-PASS-as-required-status plan.
#
# Technical owner (the only GitHub account) is the repo owner; logical role owners are in comments.

*                       @StaithValanthis

